features: SOLID STAINLESS STEEL CONSTRUCTION- Air fryer rack are made of food grade high quality 304 stainless steel, FDA Approval, BPA free, no worry about any hazardous chemicals. Durable and heat resistant, won't rust, warp or bend.

MAKES PREPARING MEALS EASIER- Double Layer rack with 5 skewers, which can put some vegetable and meat shish kabobs on the top layer. Stackable rack maximize the cooking area, allow you to cook even more, and keep the sticky food away from button of the air fryer.
OPTIMAL AIR CIRCULATION- Two layers of elevated stainless steel layers with perfect spaced grid size for optimal air circulation, even cooking, and golden crisping on all sides of your food.

EASY TO CLEAN & STORE- NO stick and no rust food grade stainless steel construction can stand up to daily using and clean, easy to clean, Dishwasher safe for fast and hassle free clean up. Raised design on each rack, can be stacked for storage easily and save more countertop space.

100% COMPATIBLE WITH- The skewer rack size: 7.8*2.75in, the metal holder size: 7.8*1.2in; Fit for Philips, Ninjia, Cosori, GoWISE USA, Cozyna, Gowise 5.3-5.8 QT XL airfye, Instant pot, power cooker; We provide life-time warrant for free return and exchanges.
body.description: HSimple XL Air Fryer Accessories, Air Fryer Double Layer Rack with 5 Skewers, Stackable Metal Holder. Fry your favorite foods with hardly any oil! Cooking more delicious food with this air fryer rack set. Made of food grade 304 material, Heavyweight chrome wire for durability, it’s oven safe to 500-degrees Fahrenheit, won’t scratch surfaces and resists rust.
